8. ENFORCEMENT

Violation of this license — particularly unauthorized commercial use,
removal of attribution, or humanitarian use that contradicts the values
of Human Flag — terminates your rights immediately and without notice.

The Author reserves the right to:

a) Demand immediate cessation of use upon violation.

b) Claim financial damages and compensation for any commercial benefit
   obtained through unauthorized use of this Software.

c) Pursue legal remedies in any jurisdiction where this Software
   is used, with the assistance of legal counsel and partner
   organizations.

d) Publicly disclose violations, including the identity of the
   violating party, as permitted by applicable law.

Ignorance of this license is not a defense.
Use of this Software implies acceptance of all terms.

